These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, soy-milk, sprite
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, domino, canasta
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, airplane, boat, van
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, musical, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, jazz, rock
House: colonial, ranch-style, victorian, gothic-revival
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, designer, dressmaker, freelancer
 1. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching adventure movies is the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person playing canasta is the ranch-style house##1
 4. the victorian house is the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the dressmaker is between the architect and the person driving the boat##2
 6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is the colonial house##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching musical movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
12. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the designer##3
13. the person playing domino is on the left of the fan of rock##1
14. the person playing canasta is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
16. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
17. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
18. the gothic-revival house is the freelancer##1
19. the fan of folk is the person playing backgammon##1
20. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
21. the person watching adventure movies is the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | sprite        | soy-milk   | 7up         | iced-tea  |
| Game          | domino         | scrabble   | backgammon   | canasta |
| Transport         | boat | airplane    | van | bus   |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | adventure  | satire      | musical   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz          | rock       | folk        | ambient   |
| House           | gothic-revival        | victorian      | colonial    | ranch-style    |
| Job         | freelancer | dressmaker | architect      | designer   |

