 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4
10. the person who likes amber is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
